{"tid":276760,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老娘的草根飯堂 - 酒梅山楂生炒骨","createTime":"2017-06-09T05:20:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-14T16:35:47.000Z","uid":30742,"like":28,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"339f35c402864ac4712575227ed14d5947096bdd","tid":276760,"uid":30742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T05:20:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/NxblG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FNxblG.jpg&h=65bb633f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MDqLZFPEUQc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMDqLZFPEUQc&d=AbalyyZSjWnhX2IyPP99JL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=b1ef8cfa\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MDqLZFPEUQc</a><br />\n<br />\n生炒骨呢咪嘢其實我做過好多次！<br />\n每次都唔係好滿意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，唔係唔夠脆口就係個醬唔多岩味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢次特登走去買包山楂片就較個汁，終於係我想要個味喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！！<br />\n再加埋自己醃既酒梅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！（其實是浸梅酒剩低既，我一直用糖浸起一樽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n又變左另一個風味，其實我覺得唔落都好食！<br />\n唔洗特登去搵，但有我會落少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ～<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n酒梅山楂生炒骨圖文食譜:&nbsp; <br />\n<a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/2017/06/sweet-and-sour-pork-ribs.html\" data-sr-url