ry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇見都心酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要收埋個籠<br />\n<br />\n我而家一望到又諗起佢走落黎平台要零食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}